#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:3
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "简介"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:5
msgid ""
"GLM-4.x series models use a Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) architecture and are"
" foundational models specifically designed for agent applications."
msgstr "GLM-4.x 系列模型采用混合专家（MoE）架构，是专门为智能体应用设计的基础模型。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:7
msgid "The `GLM-4.5` model is first supported in `vllm-ascend:v0.10.0rc1`."
msgstr "`GLM-4.5` 模型从 `vllm-ascend:v0.10.0rc1` 版本开始首次支持。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:9
msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, "
"including supported features, feature configuration, environment "
"preparation, single-node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and "
"performance evaluation."
msgstr ""
"本文档将展示模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点和多节点部署、精度评估和性能评估。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:11
msgid "Supported Features"
msgstr "支持的特性"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:13
msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the"
" model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参阅[支持的特性矩阵](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型支持的特性列表。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:15
msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get "
"the feature's configuration."
msgstr ""
"请参阅[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

#: ../../source/tutorials/models/GLM4.x.md:17
msgid "Environment Preparation"
msgstr "环境准备"

